['@MJforTexas Campaign Launches Aggressive Seven-Figure Statewide Outreach Effort to Mobilize Black Voters (Link in Bio - StyleMagazine.com) 

The MJ For Texas campaign is launching an aggressive seven-figure statewide outreach effort to mobilize Black voters across Texas. The effort will utilize Black radio, Black newspapers, mail, and digital to reach Black voters across the state and encourage them to vote for MJ Hegar on November 3rd.
